@bunthius Few questions about stealth mechanic if you feel comfortable sharing at this stage-

Is stealth mechanic going to be active at C4 launch,Is the heat sink component on ships the driver of stealth? If so, are you envisioning a direct correlation between size of heat sink and stealth- meaning, commander class heat sinks provides a higher fleet stealth rating than a medium size heat sink?,Are the scanner arrays gunna be the counter to stealth? If so, would a commander size scanner array counter the stealth rating of an opposing ship with a commander size heat sink?,
Fundamentally, i'm curious what drives the rating of a fleet's stealth rating and also the component responsible for countering stealth
